Hi,
I'm on windows. The android example runs pretty straight forward, however using this build the native libraries are pre-built and stripped of symbols and I can't use them to link other native C++ code that uses either the C++ or C TF APIs.
Do you have any suggestions other than use a different operation system for the compilation?

Thanks.
